Program: Omnibus
Title: Edward Lear
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p0376jk5
Last Broadcast Date: 31 October 1988
A look at the sad life of writer, poet, illustrator and musician Edward Lear. He was the 20th child of a London stockbroker and was raised by one of his sisters. With contributions from Lear's biographer Vivien Noakes.